snippet.title: Nemesis: Distress - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Nemesis: Distress is a new first-person multiplayer horror game based on the popular board game Nemesis. Every player has their own unique agenda in the 40-minute, unique-every-time scenarios. Also don't miss the crowdfunding campaign for Nemesis Lockdown, now on Kickstarter.

#ign
